00:40:17.900 --> 00:40:18.990
No te conozco,

00:40:19.010 --> 00:40:19.770
vete.

00:40:20.500 --> 00:40:21.290
No, Huzi.

00:40:23.760 --> 00:40:25.320
Huzi, Huzi.

00:40:26.450 --> 00:40:27.410
Piénsalo bien.

00:40:27.440 --> 00:40:28.280
¿Por qué estás aquí?

00:40:28.660 --> 00:40:29.510
